OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly dry day, with plenty
OL,6,Fof sunny spells. An afternoon heavy
OL,7,Fshower may be possible in the east.
OL,8,FStaying warm, locally hot in the east,
OL,9,Fbut a fresher feel for Cornwall with
OL,10,Fsome mist along the coast here.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA largely dry evening and
OL,13,Fnight with plenty of clear spells.
OL,14,FSome low cloud developing over the
OL,15,Fhills during the early hours. Staying
OL,16,Fmild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
